==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|simultaneities|-}}

# The quality or state of being [[simultaneous]]; [[simultaneousness]].
# {{context|music}} More than one complete musical texture occurring at the same time. This first appeared in the music of [[w:Charles Ives|Charles Ives]], and is common in the music of [[w:Conlon Nancarrow|Conlon Nancarrow]], and others.

